{"tid":2082731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警自己仆街 同袍大為緊張 向市民記者9噴胡椒噴霧","createTime":"2020-06-28T09:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T10:09:11.000Z","uid":321059,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c58d2b68fb66560ef5ea0e77b4bb596d3de46d7e","tid":2082731,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:16:48.000Z","msg":"【1650 旺角】<br />\n兆萬中心外，一群防暴警員拉起封鎖線。有目擊市民指，<span style=\"color: red;\">一名警員疑失重心跌倒，有警員見狀大為緊張，在沒有警告下向記者及市民施放胡椒噴劑，多人中椒不適。</span>之後警方舉藍旗，稱行人路上記者及市民正參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0kvmNG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0kvmNG.png&h=b2f9293a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159196781117448/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10159196781117448%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=28e2cce6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159196781117448/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己唔小心仆街 就大為緊張起哂桿咁<br />\n班狗啲心理壓力應該真係好撚大</span></span>"},{"pid":"a4501f442908b70d6087fe173f4ec88843f5340b","tid":2082731,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:18:47.000Z","msg":"隻肥popo好似比自己友推跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63708275ad279d6e861f10da31b427f620eb25c","tid":2082731,"uid":214502,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"呢D咪叫精神有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c047a9c5d960a35a48758aeb31b6abeb83bb8db2","tid":2082731,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:21:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe5ad46e7f89ef433546784622e200d538c6ae5e","tid":2082731,"uid":134061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":